                                            <width>0.40</width>
                                            <height>0.155</height>
                                            <depth/>
                                        </dimensions>), symmetrically along the central axis.</layout>
                            </layoutDesc>
                        </objectDesc>
                        <handDesc>
                            <handNote><height>0.03</height>; serifs, upsilon with rather short vertical stroke, sigma moderately slantering.</handNote>
